title: Sumo Salad
typeOfFood: Lacto, Raw, Western, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Quick service salad restaurant chain. Vegan choices include 5 salads, raisin toast, soups (in winter), fruit salad, and cold pressed juices. Labels which dishes are vegan and caters for a range of dietary requirements, all listed on the menu. Can't build your own salad as they are pre-made.
